Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.12,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)\pos(444.43,936)}凱迪爾的農場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們從今天開始就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,來打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給你們同樣的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要好好合作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我來說一下你們的工作內容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 你覺得這裡是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,森林…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是未來的小麥田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這片森林是我的財產
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它租給你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,租？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對 交給你們來打理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要開墾 耕種這片土地 收穫作物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我會以合理的價格買下作物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果購買作物的錢超過了你們自身的價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就自己買下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,自己買下自己…也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,自由…能成為自由身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,靠自己的力量 走正規的程序獲得自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你們夠努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,三年之內或許就能實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,地租就等第一次收穫再交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有煩惱和疑問 可以問這個帕提爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他很了解這座農場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是用同樣的方法成為了自由人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然身在異鄉 會有許多困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天就看托爾芬幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,長途跋涉一定也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,托爾芬 你要多多關照艾納爾啊 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 老爺他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 老爺是怎樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,丹麥都是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的故鄉也有奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但奴隸一輩子都是奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的故鄉是英格蘭北部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,冰島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,冰島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冰島…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,砍了挺多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊全都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊不是有條河嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,河這邊全都是要砍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,河的…這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺不是讓你看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想盡早獲得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去砍遠一點的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓樹倒下的方向垂直於河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是要推到河裡運走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 這裡有沒有午飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是要自己去拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 幫工的人等會送來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 還挺周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的 只有你沒幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我今晚去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,去被甩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是那個新來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一臉蠢相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奴隸相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你們好 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,知道 聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那就今晚行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,說了是你們的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這麼點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 你有意見？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人就這麼點？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 你是第一次當奴隸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那你記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能吃上飯就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而我們這些自由民還特地給你們送飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,首先當然是要表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,「非常感謝」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你這眼神是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,托爾芬 教教他禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 別傷了馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,居然在午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們搞什麼啊 就是來偷懶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是奴隸 也別對他們百依百順
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 你從後面推
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在前面拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拉到河邊把它們綁成木筏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這棵樹要不要多砍幾段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一頭老馬 拉不動的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,樹是老爺的財產
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不能擅自砍短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 這不是他們的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一般不會給奴隸用馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且只有這麼一頭老馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 把前面抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,餓得嘴裡反酸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對饒不了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,居然吃了我的午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,幫工不就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自己沒有田地 只能給老爺當幫傭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就和奴隸差不多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是比上不足比下有餘 就欺負我們找安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,托爾芬 你也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可是老爺的財產
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,區區幫工 無權使喚我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向老爺告狀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,告狀只會讓他們變本加厲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 艾納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第一天感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺 我有事報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 農場裡的幫…工…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 你要報告什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的話 我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不報告了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,水來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,剛從泉眼打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冰涼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,給我來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,急轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,請喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去了深處的泉眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在中午之前收完這一片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺居然親自幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為富人都不自己幹活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是丹人還是英格蘭人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,幹起活來都是一個樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要我說多少遍啊 奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊 我在照你說的做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,用短鐮刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 麥稈要留長一點 留到膝蓋的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前教過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,割下來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,割完麥子就是放牧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把麥稈留長 是為了給家畜吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你都17歲了 還沒記住完整的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不明白每一道工序的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了 我知道好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我流程記得很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,聽人說話時要謙虛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個樣子 作為立於人上的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好 膝蓋下面是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢貨 你怎麼能這麼揮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,麥子會被砍壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.66,zhu,,0,0,0,,留膝蓋那麼高不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那人誰啊 把老爺氣成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是老爺的兒子 奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,父子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虧我偶爾來幫個忙 你就在這嘰嘰歪歪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,虧我本來還想幫你 還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 你去哪裡 奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去沒有你的地方 臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你今後可是要繼承這座農場的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出點責任感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒求你讓我繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大老爺們居然在這磨磨嘰嘰磨磨嘰嘰磨磨嘰嘰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,誰要在這幹農活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276,1060)}我要用劍闖出一片天地啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(417.33,1060)}奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(417.33,1060)}給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去英格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就最近 絕對要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不要在這窮鄉僻壤待一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加入克努特王弟殿下的軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,立下一個又一個戰功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺 最近是指什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,最 最近就是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不久後 哈拉爾德國王就會召集援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得您還是繼承農場比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼你都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擔心您…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好樣的 幹得漂亮 女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我給少爺送吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,噓 噓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,先別去打擾 他們開始第二輪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這下子 咱家也就安穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只要少爺一直來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您您您這是怎麼了 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我家女兒冒犯您了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你們打的什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,窮鬼租地農
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不就是想要老爸的財產嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和凱迪爾家攀親戚就能財源滾滾了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女人一個個都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺 我們沒有這個意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺 留步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的 一個個都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老爸的附屬品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 待在哪裡都不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,您在做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上跑馬很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你們又在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你好好走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去找了那個女人 結果被幫工搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.22,zhu,,0,0,0,,所以在喝悶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 踩到麥子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 如果跟他們鬧 又會被大哥罵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是受不了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真羨慕少爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在這座農場裡 可以想幹啥就幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你們哪裡懂我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,生氣了？生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您有煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒閒到有空搭理你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你們趕緊回營地睡覺去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀哎呀 哎呀哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,彆氣沖沖的啦 您還這麼年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別牽馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,再喝幾杯吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚就讓咱們聊到天明吧 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,向我們傾訴青春的煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你們只是想拿我當下酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去 把馬放開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老實繼承農場不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他不了解戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是覺得戰士很威風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,打仗的人 都是禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧 明天還要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前住的村子 兩度被軍隊襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,英格蘭國王的軍隊 把村裡的房子都燒毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸和他們戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能眼睜睜看著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,第二次 是丹人的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他們藉口從英格蘭國王的惡政下解救人民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,實際卻是燒殺搶掠 無惡不作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他們簡直是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,披著人皮的禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.55,0:25:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「蛇」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
